      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to a medium bowl – this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>basa pieces</strong> and give everything a good mix up, then set aside until later</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1644324393361-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
