            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat with enough <strong>vegetable oil</strong> to cover the bottom of the pan</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated basa pieces</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until browned – this is your <strong>basa karaage</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
